itemLabel: Henry Bulwer, 1st Baron Dalling and Bulwer
itemDescription: British Liberal politician, diplomat and writer (1801-1872)

wikipedia_page.main: (William) Henry Lytton Earle Bulwer, 1st Baron Dalling and Bulwer GCB, PC (13 February 1801 – 23 May 1872) was a British Liberal politician, diplomat and writer.
